    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{dd52cced-0693-40f8-b25e-1f2f10354156}{118}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Depending on the environment, Adult Education (AE) learners might not feel comfortable&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;disclosing a&amp;nbsp;diagnosis of a disability. This is especially true for AE learners at work. Disclosure&amp;nbsp;can&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;build agency, if the learner&amp;nbsp;feels comfortable and has language they can honestly share about their&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;experiences and their needs. It is important to&amp;nbsp;help AE learners understand their rights around&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;disclosure and that they are the ones sharing and leading the conversation&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9955@$" target="_blank"&gt;(McKinney &amp;amp; Swartz, 2021)&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{dd52cced-0693-40f8-b25e-1f2f10354156}{121}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Resources.png" alt="" width="68" height="66" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_middle"&gt;​&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Additional Resource:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,," data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://courses.lincs.ed.gov/enrol/index.php?id=158" target="_blank"&gt;Legal Issues, Self-Disclosure, and Confidentiality&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(An additional resource in LINCS which requires logging in.)&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
